  Middleware

    For inbetween Server & Routes (Get,post,put,patch,delete)

  What does it do?
    -> Pre-process the request. Change aspects of requests or perform various actions
    -> Can log the requests. IE: Time it took to come through, type, status, etc
    -> Authentication before letting it through
    -> Identify & process errors

  Common middleware in Node & Express backend - "body-parser"
    -> Commonly used to handle form data - such as login form on website


